HEADWORD: Dog-faced
<hw>Dog"-faced`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having a face
resembling that of a dog.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Dog-faced baboon</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>any
